textAnnotations.description:
ldiot BOX
THE PIECE OF PAPER THAT DID NOTHING
Matt Bors
WHILE ITS' SPECIFIC ORIGIN IS
UNKNOWN, THE PIECE OF PAPER
THAT DID NOTHING BEGAN AS A
TREE BEFORE BEING TURNED
INTO A BLANK SHEET. AT THIS
POINT A PIECE OF PAPER CAN
BECOME ANYTHING.
IT TRAVELED WITH MANY OTHER EVENTUALLY, WORDS WERE PUT
SHEETS TO AN OFFICE. OTHER
PIECES OF PAPER WOULD BECOME MEANT WAS NOTHING
LAWS, SPEECHES, MEMOS AND
DOODLES. THIS PIECE OF
PAPER WOULD BECOME FAR LESS
ON IT AND WHAT THOSE WORDS
8
NON BINDING
RESOULUTION
IT WAS THEN GIVEN TO THE MAN
VERY FEW PIECES OF PAPER
MUCH PONTIFICATION AND DEBATE
SURROUNDED THE PAPER. MILLIONS | | IT WAS INTENDED FOR, AS IVE | | HAVE DONE LESS
OF WORDS WERE PUT ON MILLIONS EXPLAINED, IT MEANT NOTHING
OF OTHER PIECES OF PAPER
DISCUSSING IT. POLITICIANS
TRUMPETED AND CONDEMNED IT
AND THERE IS NO REASON TO
PAY ATTENTION TO A PIECE OF
PAPER LIKE THAT
